## 3. D3D11 gates (exact)

### Gate 1 — snapshot: `psSlot` / `valid`

```85:85:src/engine/client/application/Direct3d11/src/win32/Direct3d11_LightManager.cpp
	s_pixelDot3State.valid = false;
```

```176:196:src/engine/client/application/Direct3d11/src/win32/Direct3d11_LightManager.cpp
	if (psSlot)
	{
		// ... populate localDirectionWorld, diffuse, specular, hemispheric ...
		s_pixelDot3State.valid = true;
	}
```

No `T_parallel` in the incoming `lightList` → `psSlot` stays null → **`valid` remains false**. Dot3 fields (`localDirectionWorld`, `diffuseColor`, `backColor`, etc.) are **not cleared** on that call — only `valid` is flipped.

### Gate 2 — PS Producer B: `d3.valid`

```945:957:src/engine/client/application/Direct3d11/src/win32/Direct3d11_StaticShaderData.cpp
						if (d3.valid)
						{
							// ... object-local c0 = (-localDir, specPower) ...
							std::memcpy(staging.data() + PSCR_dot3LightDirection               * 16, &c0, ...);
							std::memcpy(staging.data() + PSCR_dot3LightDiffuseColor             * 16, &d3.diffuseColor, ...);
							std::memcpy(staging.data() + PSCR_dot3LightSpecularColor            * 16, &d3.specularColor, ...);
							std::memcpy(staging.data() + PSCR_dot3LightTangentMinusDiffuseColor * 16, &d3.tangentMinusDiffuseColor, ...);
							std::memcpy(staging.data() + PSCR_dot3LightTangentMinusBackColor    * 16, &d3.tangentMinusBackColor, ...);
						}
```

When `!d3.valid`, staging is seeded from the persistent shadow (`:907-911`) and **c0–c4 are not refreshed** for this draw.

### Gate 3 — VS Producer A: `d3.valid` in `composeSlot0Shadow`

```380:415:src/engine/client/application/Direct3d11/src/win32/Direct3d11_StateCache.cpp
			s_slot0Shadow.lightData[0] = d3.ambient;

			if (d3.valid)
			{
				// parallelSpecular[0] @ c17-c19
				// dot3 @ c40-c43
				// extendedLightData @ c60-c63
			}
```

`parallel[0..1]` @ c20–c23 are filled **outside** the `d3.valid` gate (`:425-430`).

